.games.index
  - if @presenter.has_games?
    - @presenter.games.each do |game|
      .game
        .detail
          .label Board:
          .content= game.board

        .detail
          .label Time left:
          .content= humanize_duration(game.time_left)

        .detail
          .label Points:
          .content= game.points

        .link-to-play
          = link_to "Play!", game_path(game.id)
  - else
    .no-games
      | No active games yet! Try creating one via the API.
